uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.util.stats
Class ExperimentalDataSeries

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.qmul.sbcs.evolution.convergence.util.stats.ExperimentalDataSeries

public class ExperimentalDataSeries
extends java.lang.Object

Since:
02 March, 2012
Author:
Joe Parker
See Also:
This class is intended to provide basic utility methods for a vector of float data. This class is an experimental adaptation of the DataSeries class that should (!) give better data binning etc
